Ormat Technologies Gets Geothermal Contracts in New Zealand

-- B y   D a v i d   A l t a n e r
-- 
2011-06-08T07:06:39Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-08/ormat-technologies-gets-geothermal-contracts-in-new-zealand.html
Ormat Technologies Inc. (ORA)  said it
received supply, engineering, procurement and construction
contracts with Mighty River Power Ltd. of  New Zealand  for the
first stage of the Ngatamariki geothermal project valued at a
total of approximately $130 million.  To contact the reporter on this story:
David Altaner in London at 
 daltaner@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Maria Ermakova at 
 mermakova@bloomberg.net  